high_descs: Go to the coffeemaker
Pick up the knife near the coffeemaker
Go to the stove
Cut the potato
Go to the coffeemaker
Put the knife down on the coffeemaker table
Go to the cut potato
Pick up a potato slice
Go to the sink
Wash the potato slice
Go to the coffeemaker
Put the potato down on the coffeemaker table
anns.task_desc: Put a washed potato slice down on a table

high_descs: Turn right towards the table with the coffee maker.
Pick up the knife on the cup.
Turn left and go to the stove.
Cut the potato on the right of the stove.
Turn left and go back to the white table.
Stand the knife up in front of thee cup on the table.
Turn left and go back to the stove.
Pick up a slice of potato on the right of the stove.
Turn around and go to the sink.
Rinse off the potato slice in the left sink and pick it back up.
Turn around and go to the white table.
Put the potato slice on the white table to the left of the knife.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean slice of potato on the table.

high_descs: Move slightly forward and turn right to face the white table with the coffee maker.
Pick up the sharp knife with yellow handle between the two coffee mugs.
Turn left and carry the knife to stand in front of the stove.
Use the knife to slice the potato on the counter to the right of the stove.
Turn back around and carry the knife to the white table with the coffee maker.
Place the knife standing up on the table in front of the mug closest to you.
Turn left to return to stand in front of the stove.
Pick up a slice of potato from the counter.
Turn around to cross the room to the fridge, then head right to the sink.
Place the potato slice in the left side of the sink, turn on the water, and then remove.
Turn and carry the potato slice to the white table with the coffee maker.
Place the potato slice on the table to the left of the knife you previously left there.
anns.task_desc: Move a washed slice of potato to the white table.
